{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/posts/2020-09-24-hades","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"b5623d19-1526-550b-aa09-741c61ff6e94","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f565075f408fe980f6f9fdb65ffb0334/eea4a/hades_by_jenzee.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 136%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Hades\"\n        title=\"Hades\"\n        src=\"/static/f565075f408fe980f6f9fdb65ffb0334/29d31/hades_by_jenzee.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f565075f408fe980f6f9fdb65ffb0334/e52aa/hades_by_jenzee.jpg 175w,\n/static/f565075f408fe980f6f9fdb65ffb0334/70ebb/hades_by_jenzee.jpg 350w,\n/static/f565075f408fe980f6f9fdb65ffb0334/29d31/hades_by_jenzee.jpg 700w,\n/static/f565075f408fe980f6f9fdb65ffb0334/9ecec/hades_by_jenzee.jpg 1050w,\n/static/f565075f408fe980f6f9fdb65ffb0334/eea4a/hades_by_jenzee.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>The latest game from my favoritest studio, <a href=\"https://www.supergiantgames.com/games/hades/\">Hades</a>, is a refined culmination of <a href=\"https://www.supergiantgames.com/\">Supergiant Games</a>’ craft: impeccable stunning artwork, epic cinematic soundtrack, tight crispy combat, tough-as-nails gameplay, lovingly written characters, and finally a wonderful touching story at the center.</p>\n<p><em>Supergiant</em>’s previous titles all tell of a memorable touching story. With such a precious piece of artwork, for me, is something to be played once, experienced once, something to commit as a beautiful memory, not to be replayed.</p>\n<p>However, at the core, what sets <em>Hades</em> apart is its <em>replayability</em>. It is here that the devs did something novel. They created a roguelike game, intentionally repetitive in nature. However, unlike the usual formula of using mechanics as the reward (like unlockable items or skills), <em>Hades</em> instead uses <em>story as the reward</em>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0d51ce87fb81fc6ea04054aa01a566d7/0f98f/hades_screenshot.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screenshot\"\n        title=\"Screenshot\"\n        src=\"/static/0d51ce87fb81fc6ea04054aa01a566d7/29d31/hades_screenshot.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0d51ce87fb81fc6ea04054aa01a566d7/e52aa/hades_screenshot.jpg 175w,\n/static/0d51ce87fb81fc6ea04054aa01a566d7/70ebb/hades_screenshot.jpg 350w,\n/static/0d51ce87fb81fc6ea04054aa01a566d7/29d31/hades_screenshot.jpg 700w,\n/static/0d51ce87fb81fc6ea04054aa01a566d7/9ecec/hades_screenshot.jpg 1050w,\n/static/0d51ce87fb81fc6ea04054aa01a566d7/d165a/hades_screenshot.jpg 1400w,\n/static/0d51ce87fb81fc6ea04054aa01a566d7/0f98f/hades_screenshot.jpg 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>In this novel manner, they carry out their signature character-based story-telling. In this manner, they’ve created their most replayable game yet: they keep the player coming back, grinding, replaying the levels over and over, just to get a little further, just to learn a little more about this character, who are they, what happened to them, and why are they here?</p>\n<p>Moreover, they’ve ingeniously chosen the rich world of Greek mythology as the setting for this cyclical mechanic: the main character, born of gods, is immortal, unable to die, and therefore forced to relive death over and over as the player fails to escape.</p>\n<p>This is <em>Supergiant</em>’s signature trademark: their ability to craft a <em>complete</em> game. By that I mean, a game where no aspect is lacking, nor is any aspect shining brighter than the rest. Whether it is art, music, gameplay, or writing, they are each so strong on their own, but when woven together, becomes something so powerful, so immersive, so beautiful and memorable, a complete story.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/65da604d08311050fe20aa353f04b14c/8ec0a/hades_sunrise.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screenshot\"\n        title=\"Screenshot\"\n        src=\"/static/65da604d08311050fe20aa353f04b14c/29d31/hades_sunrise.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/65da604d08311050fe20aa353f04b14c/e52aa/hades_sunrise.jpg 175w,\n/static/65da604d08311050fe20aa353f04b14c/70ebb/hades_sunrise.jpg 350w,\n/static/65da604d08311050fe20aa353f04b14c/29d31/hades_sunrise.jpg 700w,\n/static/65da604d08311050fe20aa353f04b14c/9ecec/hades_sunrise.jpg 1050w,\n/static/65da604d08311050fe20aa353f04b14c/d165a/hades_sunrise.jpg 1400w,\n/static/65da604d08311050fe20aa353f04b14c/8ec0a/hades_sunrise.jpg 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Hades","date":"September 24, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2020-09-24-hades","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/posts/2020-01-05-expensive-wine-is-overrated","type":"post"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Expensive wine is overrated"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}